: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区绿化养护及各院区室内绿化招租服务；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区、北区、五官科医院、紫薇门诊及皮肤科专科医院、盐城市儿童医院；</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、招标范</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">围及内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区绿化养护及各院区室内绿化招租服务，具体详见招标人的要求和工程量清单。招标人保留调整绿化种类的权利，中标人须无条件服从。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、招标规模：捌万元整<span>/</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、服务期：<span>1</span>年，合同按年签订。经招标人年度考核合格后，可续签下一年合同，最多续签二次；考核不合格的，招标人有权立即终止合同。具体开始日期以招标人的书面通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace:; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph; punctuation-wrap: simple;\'><b><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、投标人应具备相应的绿化出租及养护服务能力的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、投标人须具备自营苗木花场场所，营业注册地为盐城地区（投标时提供相关证明材料）。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; -ms-layout-